ermal/] dla ataków wielokrotnych) spowodowania [abilityred]zwęglenia[/abilityred] na {durationCharred}[turn/].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LASER_FOCUS_MODULE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Laser Precision Module</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Moduł precyzji laserowej</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LASER_FOCUS_MODULE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit's ranged Laser weapons gain +{Range} range.[br/]Additionally this unit's weapons gain +{AccuracyBoost}% accuracy.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Dystansowe uzbrojenie laserowe tej jednostki zyskuje +{Range} zasięgu.[br/]Ponadto uzbrojenie jednostki zyskuje +{AccuracyBoost}% do celności.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">In the text below, any inserted strings - anything of the form {text} - is replaced by an integer value for the thing described in the brackets. If the {text} is not followed by a unit - e.g. shields, hitpoints - the icon for the unit is inserted together with the integer. The same holds for symbols - e.g. '+', '%' - which are occasionally inserted together with the integer.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">For references to game terminology and in-world references, please check the glossary delivered as part of the documentation.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="Stri